config SIMPLEBUTTON
	tristate "Simple Energy simulated hardware button driver"
	depends on MISC_DEVICES
	help
	  This driver simulates a physical hardware button for Android
	  platform stack testing. It exposes sysfs nodes under
	  /sys/class/misc/simplebutton/ and supports ioctl and poll.

	  Say Y to build into the kernel, or M to build as a loadable module.
